      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that gets the job done? This honest daily driver is a dependable choice for anyone prioritizing utility and value! While it shows some clear signs of its journey through life with visible wear and tear, it remains a functional and hardworking companion ready for its next owner. It\u2019s a great opportunity to get a reliable set of wheels at an accessible price!",
