    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated mechanic or someone looking for a major restoration project. The engine currently exhibits a loud knocking sound and has multiple active oil leaks, suggesting internal damage that will require a complete overhaul. The body shows significant signs of age, including several rust spots on the rocker panels and a large dent in the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears in the seats and a non-functional climate control system. It is being sold strictly as-is, and we recommend towing it from the lot.",
