      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of uncompromising caliber. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies even the most discerning collector. Every surface and mechanical component has been maintained to an exacting degree, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For the individual who demands excellence without exception, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
