    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, keeping it garage-parked and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and drives like a dream, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
