    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated double-VANOS system. This chassis has undergone rigorous inspection, confirming a pristine subframe and optimal compression across all cylinders. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp-shifting manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, maintains factory-spec rigidity. The original paint exhibits exceptional depth and luster, complemented by an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrumentation. A turn-key example for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
