    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly superlative example of automotive preservation. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its original deep luster with no evidence of road rash, swirl marks, or imperfections; it has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, free of any curb contact, and are fitted with premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear or creasing, while the high-tech interface and switchgear function with the crispness of a new car. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It boasts a comprehensive, documented service history with every maintenance interval performed exclusively by certified technicians. There are no leaks, no noises, and the engine bay is clean enough to display. For the buyer seeking a collector-grade vehicle that requires absolutely no apologies, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
